name: Unknown Bike Co PS1 Frame
description: We did it. We made a pursuit frame... and it's light... and its stiff. Weighs in at 3.6 lbs and constructed from 6061-T6 Aluminum with a custom molded downtube that tapers to a horizontal flat where it meets the bottom bracket shell.
